    <item>
      <title>凯雷准备在投资领域实现“多次”退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/carlyle-ready-to-make-a-number-of-exits-in-investments-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯雷集团美洲企业私募股权联席主管 Brian Bernasek 表示，随着私募股权交易市场反弹，凯雷集团正准备退出“大量”投资。他表示，强劲的信贷市场和稳定的利率是部分原因。他接受了彭博社 Sonali Basak 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-12/carlyle-ready-to-make-a-number-of-exits-in-investments-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 18:03:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stifel 关闭卡尔加里办事处，削减多伦多银行家职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/stifel-shuts-calgary-office-cuts-investment-bank-jobs-in-canada</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯蒂费尔金融公司 (Stifel Financial Corp.) 关闭了其卡尔加里办事处，结束了加拿大石油行业能源投资银行业务的辉煌，同时还解雇了多伦多的一些投资银行家和分析师。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/stifel-shuts-calgary-office-cuts-investment-bank-jobs-in-canada</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:47:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
